Package ohos.data.search.model

Interface IndexType


  • public interface IndexType
    Represents the index type of an index attribute.

    You can call IndexForm.setIndexType(String) to specify the index type for an index attribute.

    Since:
    3
    SystemCapability
    SystemCapability.Data#DATA_SEARCH

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field Description
      static String ANALYZED
      The index field is indexed, and the field value is analyzed.
      static String ANALYZED_NO_NORMS
      The index field is indexed, the field value is analyzed, and Norms is ignored.
      static String DOUBLE
      The index field is indexed as a double value, which can be searched by specifying a range.
